	<h3>
	Original members
	</h3>
	<p> 
		The Kleine seminar was created in the summer of 2019 by a like-minded group of PhD candidates and postdoc researchers with interest
		in representation theory. You can find their names below.
	<u1>
		<li>Sigiswald Barbier</li>
		<li>Asmus Bisbo</li>
		<li>Sam Claerebout</li>
